thread.title: BRIEF-Shunya International Brand Consulting Beijing sees FY 2017 net profit up 17.19 pct to 46.14 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shunya International Brand Consulting Beijing sees FY 2017 net profit up 17.19 pct to 46.14 pct

organizations.name: shunya international brand consulting beijing co ltd

text:
Jan 30(Reuters) - Shunya International Brand Consulting Beijing Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 17.19 percent to 46.14 percent, or to be 68.8 million yuan to 85.8 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 58.7 million yuan
* The reasons for the forecast are expanded business and increased project income Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/1RSR59 Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
